dc_description_s: This line data layer represents hydrography for Manitowoc County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Manitowoc_HydroLine_2016.gdb.[Rivers, streams, and creeks in Manitowoc County. Features were delineated using Manitowoc County's 2010 digital orthophotograph.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
